1.) Either replace /lib/netifd/hostapd.sh with these files (matching your OpenWrt version)
2.) Or look for the following item and chage it from:
        append bss_conf "wpa_psk_radius=2" "$N"
    To:
        append bss_conf "wpa_psk_radius=3" "$N"
        
3.) In 25.12.x There is a change and it seems that /lib/netifd/hostapd.sh is not used any more (Though it still is present)
 The file now is: 
 /usr/share/ucode/wifi/ap.uc
 
 Look for:
 
(Around line 129) 
if (config.ppsk) {
        iface_authentication_server(config);
        config.macaddr_acl = 2;    
        config.wpa_psk_radius = 2;
} else if (length(config.key) == 64) {

Change to:

if (config.ppsk) {
                        iface_authentication_server(config);
        config.macaddr_acl = 2;    
        config.wpa_psk_radius = 3;
} else if (length(config.key) == 64) {

